{"tid":1717894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史既教訓]請不要對荃灣被推落樓亡既青年麻木","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:42:57.000Z","uid":43557,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57e9fff4889eb609747d1c0f2738d07f508d61fc","tid":1717894,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"香港人出名係三分鐘熱度<br />\n永遠第一件事發生既時候係最大反應同反彈<br />\n但當有第二件事發生 香港人已經會感到麻木<br />\n爆眼少女被射盲眼個個幫佢討回公道<br />\n但當有第二個被射盲眼 大家都已經習慣左咁<br />\n我係呢度求下大家唔好做習慣撚麻木撚<br />\n周同學被推落樓死大家都好嬲同出黎幫佢報仇<br />\n荃灣呢個青年請大家仲有呢個憤怒既心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好對不公義既事習慣同麻木</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ff82522ce8738b9bca29b83d18340eb51e76797","tid":1717894,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"[和你勇文宣升級！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲好嬲好嬲，但文宣更要更快更有效做好，要拉攏最多人過黎同對方憾過，我地從來都唔係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e5491fd69ab0f775725813f24f7767923b5e50d","tid":1717894,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"人命黎架屌"},{"pid":"ff78506fbf8e145fb1602ee3b99e8b16de198617","tid":1717894,"uid":107458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人填命，血債血償！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c98953fd9003854e0a2f015